General.Name: GCP Infrastructure Investments Limited
General.Description: GCP Infrastructure Investments Limited focuses on investing in the United Kingdom infrastructure debt. The company makes infrastructure investments through acquiring interests in debt instruments issued by infrastructure project companies. It primarily invests in senior and subordinated debt instruments. GCP Infrastructure Investments Limited was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Saint Helier, Jersey.
